=Author Bio=

ABOUT MICHEL BAUWENS:

"Michel Bauwens is the founder of the P2P Foundation and a pioneering researcher in commons-based solutions. As a thought leader in his field, he has helped cities and organizations worldwide develop plans for a future based on collaboration rather than competition. His work spans from advising governments and organizations to documenting emerging forms of social organization. Based in Chiang Mai, Thailand, he leads research on how communities can work together more effectively in our rapidly changing world."


